claim.claim-text:
A device comprising:
at least one processor; and
a memory operatively coupled to the processor, the memory storing program instructions that when executed by the processor, causes the processor to:
define a location;
detect whether a device is within proximity of the location;
provide at least one of a plurality of communication functions to the device.
